items.title: Hello (Adele song) - Wikipedia
items.snippet:
"Hello" is a song by English singer Adele, released on 23 October 2015 by XL 
Recordings as the lead single from her third studio album, 25 (2015). Adele co-

influences, and lyrics that discuss themes of nostalgia and regret. Upon release,
